original_title: Starrcast V: 30 Years Later With Bret Hart
overview: On July 30th 30 Years Later with Bret "The Hitman" Hart is coming live on FITE for SummerSlam '92 Celebration. Tune in and hear more about Bret Hart's match against 'The British Bulldog' Davey Boy Smith at WWE SummerSlam 1992 and much, much more!
title: Starrcast V: 30 Years Later With Bret Hart
